1.16
log
@pledge "stdio rpath wpath cpath exec" early, then after opening
"nohup.out" drop to "stdio exec".  from Ricardo Mestre with a tweak
to protect both code paths.
ok millert
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: nohup.c,v 1.15 2015/01/16 06:40:10 deraadt Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: nohup.c,v 1.6 1995/08/31 23:35:25 jtc Exp $	*/

/*
 * Copyright (c) 1989 The Regents of the University of California.
 * All rights reserved.
 *
 * Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without
 * modification, are permitted provided that the following conditions
 * are met:
